{"tid":531860,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【曾志偉記招】稱性侵藍潔瑛全屬捏造：願配合任形式調查","createTime":"2018-01-17T08:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T11:52:58.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f279e592beb21d91d50a1a56ea500a0bd794de5f","tid":531860,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180117/large/1516178969_cd1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180117%2Flarge%2F1516178969_cd1a.jpg&h=bc34c86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾志偉今午四時半於九龍香拉舉行記招會，回應近日性侵傳聞。志偉於4時37分現身，他身穿深色外套，波鞋，表情嚴肅，身邊有兩男子陪同。他先企定定讓傳媒拍照，之後兒子曾國祥亦有上台，以示支持。兩人俱神情凝重。<br />\n<br />\n之後曾國祥落台，一名西裝男子陪志偉開始。現場不設答問環節。<br />\n曾志偉稱，有關性侵藍潔瑛之報道，全屬捏造。曾志偉稱願接受任何形式之調查，以保聲譽。<br />\n曾志偉表示，就網上針對他的不實報道，指控嚴重，影響其個人聲譽，且影響他身邊朋友、至愛家人及子女，以及明星足球隊。為免他們受不不必要傷害，故他覺得必須回應。<br />\n曾志偉又稱，堅決用法律手段，針對他不實指控，已採取法律行動起訴。<br />\n講聲明約10分鐘，分別用廣東話同國語發表。離開前志偉向傳媒躬恭致謝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180117/57719300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F57719300&d=iyvf8w05XlyTyEHPDCLKZL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1e0ad3a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F57719300&h=17577104\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180117/57719300</a>"},{"pid":"6ff969247184ac464d7e717d304fa2254c925c6f","tid":531860,"uid":133529,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:01:00.000Z","msg":"佢就係睇死咁多年，已經驗唔到精液DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c164817a0882667508ac653a090e653111517e0","tid":531860,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"你唔提一提我都唔係好記得"},{"pid":"f79ba16151fb76465429d42c88b7ffc0372fd000","tid":531860,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"開記招都唔會有人信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca8b8985afa598a4d879bc20aaec50f3ae47573","tid":531860,"uid":145779,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:19:45.000Z","msg":"呢D記招不嬲都係得啖笑<br />\n同阿嬌話自己好天真好傻一樣"},{"pid":"5dc8af3ad4e9e34d1b291d48155236c6ba4209e6","tid":531860,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"係大陸搞到好大單？竟然開記招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7665d56ba82c7674993d5acc72a052c84f07a380","tid":531860,"uid":8717,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:34:17.000Z","msg":"還金寶湯一個清白"},{"pid":"e4f6683e10c46d6755c88d3e90cae2df5897eadc","tid":531860,"uid":555,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:40:29.000Z","msg":"點解個個都一口咬定佢有做"},{"pid":"03c1d11ae59c548e0727077da140be05ad7a7e62","tid":531860,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>還金寶湯一個清白</blockquote><br />\n兩個影壇大哥wo"},{"pid":"12457b13a53af0d97dc438e8475e588ded5e613d","tid":531860,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bo9XMtVs1Mw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBo9XMtVs1Mw&d=iyvf8w05XlyTyEHPDCLKZL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=e1665dee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bo9XMtVs1Mw</a><br />\n原片 不過名被消音<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x4vBF2VDPBg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx4vBF2VDPBg&d=iyvf8w05XlyTyEHPDCLKZL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=7cf9d2f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.co